        "title": "Why switch from Episerver? ",
        "style": "dark",
        "decorator": null,
        "content": "<p>While it does have outstanding personalization, the commerce engine itself is not the best out there and, unlike the content management platform, it is not known to be that user friendly. Also not particularly intuitive is the promotion engine that comes with the software, as it can be somewhat cumbersome to use. Finally, the Episerver developer documentation needs an upgrade, and it might make sense to look at some Episerver competitors.&nbsp;</p>\n",
